    "Table E.13 shows that coworker encouragement strongly predicts an individual worker's own reported encouragement: the first-stage coefficient is approximately 1, with an Fstatistic of 3,645.",
    "The strong correlation in reported employer encouragement at the workplace level supports our interpretation of these initiatives as centralized policies.",
